msgid "The Security Component"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../components/security.rst:7
msgid ""
"The Security component provides a complete security system for your web "
"application. It ships with facilities for authenticating using HTTP basic"
" authentication, interactive form login or X.509 certificate login, but "
"also allows you to implement your own authentication strategies. "
"Furthermore, the component provides ways to authorize authenticated users"
" based on their roles."
msgstr ""

