msgid ""
"The Security component is divided into several smaller sub-components "
"which can be used separately:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../components/security.rst:22
msgid "``symfony/security-core``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../components/security.rst:21
msgid ""
"It provides all the common security features, from authentication to "
"authorization and from encoding passwords to loading users."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../components/security.rst:26
msgid "``symfony/security-http``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../components/security.rst:25
msgid ""
"It integrates the core sub-component with the HTTP protocol to handle "
"HTTP requests and responses."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../components/security.rst:29
msgid "``symfony/security-csrf``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../components/security.rst:29
msgid "It provides protection against `CSRF attacks`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../components/security.rst:33
msgid "``symfony/security-guard``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../components/security.rst:32
msgid ""
"It brings many layers of authentication together, allowing the creation "
"of complex authentication systems."
msgstr ""

